      "title": "(a) The terms 'authentication', 'factor of authentication', 'issuer', 'merchant'",
      "text": "(a) The terms 'authentication', 'factor of authentication', 'issuer', 'merchant'\nwill have the same meaning as defined in Reserve Bank of India\n(Authentication mechanisms for digital payment transactions) Directions, 2025\ndated September 25, 2025 and Master Direction on Regulation of Payment\nAggregator (PA) dated September 15, 2025.",
