      "document_id": "MD13374",
      "title": "(d) The customer shall be given a facility to choose or change a mode among",
      "text": "(d) The customer shall be given a facility to choose or change a mode among\navailable options (SMS, email, etc.) for receiving the pre-transaction\nnotification from the issuer.",
